---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About ManifestKit — Free Spiritual Tools" description="Learn about ManifestKit and our mission to empower conscious creators with free manifestation tools.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-amber-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">About ManifestKit</span>
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-[#9B8CB8] leading-relaxed">
      <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#1A1333] border border-purple-800/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-3">🔮 Our Mission</h2>
        <p>ManifestKit exists to empower conscious creators with free, beautiful, and easy-to-use spiritual tools. We believe everyone deserves access to manifestation tools regardless of their financial situation.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#1A1333] border border-purple-800/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-3">💜 Why We Built This</h2>
        <p>We are practitioners of the Law of Attraction who wanted better tools for our own spiritual journey. When we couldn't find what we needed, we built it ourselves — and decided to share it with the world for free.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#1A1333] border border-purple-800/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-3">🌐 Our Tools</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mt-3">
          <li>⏳ <strong class="text-purple-200">Manifestation Timer</strong> — Set intentions and track your progress visually</li>
          <li>✨ <strong class="text-purple-200">Affirmation Generator</strong> — Daily personalized affirmations for any focus area</li>
          <li>🎯 <strong class="text-purple-200">Vision Board Maker</strong> — Create and export digital vision boards</li>
          <li>🌙 <strong class="text-purple-200">Moon Phase Calendar</strong> — Align your manifestations with lunar cycles</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#1A1333] border border-purple-800/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-3">🔒 Privacy First</h2>
        <p>All your data stays on your device. We use localStorage — no accounts, no tracking, no data selling. Your intentions and wishes are sacred and private.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#1A1333] border border-purple-800/40">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-3">📧 Contact</h2>
        <p>Have suggestions or just want to share your manifestation success story? We'd love to hear from you at <span class="text-amber-400">hello@manifestkit.cc.cd</span></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>